{"id": "1497316137095008508", "channel_id": "1300659552701648960", "type": 0, "author_id": "224166446853259265", "author_name": "drkseraphin", "author_bot": false, "content": "j'ai commencé seulment y'a quelques mois mais un petit conseil que j'pourais donné c'est de bien pensé a unlock les vieu events pour recupéré les poses (ulti de ton perso), perso j'ai commencé a la rerun de l'event tout a gauch dans cet onglet, et j'pense c'est le truc le plus universelement fort du jeu (+2energie et pioche 2)", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T19:19:45.872000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-24T19:22:33.124000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1497316137166438550", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2373442, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1300659552701648960/1497316137166438550/image.png?ex=69ed13d1&is=69ebc251&hm=62a41c552a8ea678e592a731fefca97e772bb9858d371e33ea7a4b6cdf9853cf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
